text: Anaesthetis confossicollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Baeckmann in 1903. It is known from Russia, China, Mongolia, Siberia and Japan.BioLib.cz - Anaesthetis confossicollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1903
